[log] bash[68] stdout ## Detailed Implementation Nodes of Functions
[log] bash[68] stdout ### Node 1: Basic Paper Search
[log] bash[68] stdout **Function Description**: Implement the basic paper search function, supporting keyword queries and result quantity limits.
[log] bash[68] stdout **Core Algorithm**:
[log] bash[68] stdout - Build an arXiv search query
[log] bash[68] stdout - Apply field specifiers to optimize the search
[log] bash[68] stdout - Process search results and format the output
[log] bash[68] stdout **Input - Output Example**:
[log] bash[68] stdout ```python
